n: Slow Cooker Wieners in Wiener BBQ Sauce
des: "This makes a great appetizer for parties, or a main dish for the hot dog lovers in your family. Serve with French fries, all the fixings, and a cold, crisp salad."
ins:
Place the wieners in a slow cooker. In a medium bowl, combine the grape jelly, mustard, brown sugar and cider vinegar. Mix well and pour over the wieners.
Cook on low setting for at least 1 hour before serving.
